===Etymology===
Latin ''abstergens'', past preterite of ''abstergere''
===Adjective===
#Serving to [[cleanse]], [[detergent]].

===Noun===
#A substance used in [[cleansing]]; a [[detergent]]; as, soap is an ''abstergent''.

